longBusinessSummary: Ybox Real Estate Ltd., formerly known as Marathon Investments SA., is a real estate investment firm specializing investments in residential projects, commercial and office buildings. The firm prefers to invest in Israel. Earlier, it operated as a a venture capital and private equity firm. Ybox Real Estate Ltd. was founded in 1993 and is based in Ashdod, Israel with additional office in Tel Aviv, Israel.
